Harold Hunter https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Harold_Hunter 0 Harold Atkins Hunter (April 2, 1974 – February 17, 2006) was an American professional skateboarder and actor. He played the role of Harold in Harmony Korine's reality-based 1995 film Kids. Harold_Atkins_Hunter ( April_2_,_1974 – February_17_,_2006 ) was an_American_professional_skateboarder_and_actor .
